      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "there is NO (accessible) <code>first</code> field in <code>ResultSet</code> !  BTW the method <code>first()</code> will throw an <code>SQLException</code> if the the result set type is <code>TYPE_FORWARD_ONLY</code> (and as already mentioned, will move the cursor)"
    } ],
