    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>By using resultSet.next() you can easily get the result, whether resultSet containing any value or not</p>\n\n<pre><code>ResultSet resultSet = preparedStatement.executeQuery();\nif(resultSet.next())\n //resultSet contain some values\nelse\n // empty resultSet\n</code></pre>\n"
