    "body" : "<p>This is a practical and easy read piece I believe.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>        if (res.next()) {\n            do {\n\n                // successfully in. do the right things.\n\n            } while (res.next());\n        } else {\n           // no results back. warn the user.\n        }\n</code></pre>\n"
